{"tid":1156846,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"侵爺宣佈國家緊急狀態 意在禁止美國公司使用「敵對勢力」通訊設備","createTime":"2019-05-16T01:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T02:15:14.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"addbe604a4548adcdb2d62f71bdca1996c9a9847","tid":1156846,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585a98e33eef88da27298c5c6e14cf8342e4ec91","tid":1156846,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:05:02.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普簽署行政命令，宣佈國家進入緊急狀態，需警惕「外國敵對勢力」對美國通訊系統造成的國家安全威脅。這一行政命令在華盛頓時間周三（5月15日）生效，被普遍認為意在禁止美國公司使用外國通訊設備，尤其針對中國的通訊巨頭華為。<br />\n這一命令賦予美國商務部權力，禁止「對國家安全製造不可接受的風險」的相關交易。<br />\n行政命令中並未提到任何具體公司或國家的名字。但外界觀察人士普遍認為，這一禁令矛頭指向華為，為未來封殺華為打下法規基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-48290413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-48290413&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2FSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=d18a8cfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-48290413&h=e0467312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-48290413</a>"},{"pid":"ac8873a20097665a0c7248b37c243095046cdd62","tid":1156846,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"In Trump we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52406c0e6d2434fd6f1f0f7492a5d34baba4fc83","tid":1156846,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"侵想行中國條舊路，封國！"}]}